HyperFLINT statically links FLINT, GMP, and MPFR (all LGPL-3.0-or-later) and
embeds mimalloc (MIT) and xxhash (BSD-2-Clause); the CLI loads libomp
(Apache-2.0 with LLVM exception) dynamically. See THIRD-PARTY-LICENSES for the
full texts. Because the complete HyperFLINT source and its build scripts are
published, and the FLINT version (3.4.0) is identified, any user may rebuild
HyperFLINT against a modified copy of these libraries, satisfying the LGPL
relink provision.
